# Self-signup email whitelist
# One email per line. Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
# Matching is case-insensitive on the full email address.
#
# Copy this file to signup_whitelist.txt and add invited emails below.
# Edits take effect immediately (the file is re-read on each signup attempt).
#
# alice@example.com
# bob@company.org
